title: Animated sonicblend
transcripts: one of the really exciting things about sonic blend is that you can use it with different kinds of makeup that you already own like liquid, powder, gel, or cream foundation. Sonic blends brush bristles move it over 400 times per second which is over 25,000 times per minute to apply makeup more evenly with better blending and without clumping and settling into pores and wrinkles we call this flawless airbrush like sonic makeup applications 3D flawfill technology which uses sonic movements to help disperse individual granules and fine layers for a seamless makeup application that is simple to use and yields flawless looking results once you've used sonic blend one of the world's first rechargeable sonic makeup brushes with antimicrobial protected brush bristles you won't want to imagine applying your makeup without it.
